Because to have intention-- so
you cannot hear-- for example,

00:57:41.520 --> 00:57:43.745 align:middle line:84%
just recently I found a
book Wayne Dyer wrote--

00:57:43.745 --> 00:57:44.620 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Wayne Dyer.

00:57:44.620 --> 00:57:45.732 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:57:45.732 --> 00:57:46.410 align:middle line:90%
Wayne Dyer.

00:57:46.410 --> 00:57:47.370 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:57:47.370 --> 00:57:49.200 align:middle line:84%
>>RADOS: You can use
intention to attain--

00:57:49.200 --> 00:57:53.650 align:middle line:84%
to achieve a good car, good
carpet, better house, better

00:57:53.650 --> 00:57:55.260 align:middle line:90%
lifestyle, this and that.

00:57:55.260 --> 00:57:57.177 align:middle line:84%
But you cannot find
yourself with intention,

00:57:57.177 --> 00:57:58.760 align:middle line:84%
because you're going
to be in tension.

00:57:58.760 --> 00:58:00.940 align:middle line:84%
So if you continue being in
tension, so you will never,

00:58:00.940 --> 00:58:01.760 align:middle line:90%
ever find yourself.

00:58:01.760 --> 00:58:03.130 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's a
tense state to be in.

00:58:03.130 --> 00:58:04.963 align:middle line:84%
>>RADOS: Being is an
intense state of being.

00:58:04.963 --> 00:58:06.580 align:middle line:84%
So you have to give
up on your tension

00:58:06.580 --> 00:58:09.326 align:middle line:90%
in order to attain nonintention.

00:58:09.326 --> 00:58:10.700 align:middle line:84%
State nonintentional
state to be.

00:58:10.700 --> 00:58:12.949 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Which is what we
were talking about earlier.

00:58:12.949 --> 00:58:14.820 align:middle line:90%
You create the idea.

00:58:14.820 --> 00:58:16.530 align:middle line:84%
You have to desire,
the motivation.

00:58:16.530 --> 00:58:18.356 align:middle line:84%
Then you put the
effort in, which

00:58:18.356 --> 00:58:19.980 align:middle line:84%
requires a certain
amount of intention,

00:58:19.980 --> 00:58:20.980 align:middle line:90%
and then let go of it.

00:58:20.980 --> 00:58:22.917 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise you remain
in tension, right?

00:58:22.917 --> 00:58:24.000 align:middle line:90%
>>RADOS: It was intention.

00:58:24.000 --> 00:58:28.750 align:middle line:84%
When you are in tension, you
are trapped in your mind.

00:58:28.750 --> 00:58:32.140 align:middle line:84%
You are in that tension between
positive and negative clashing

00:58:32.140 --> 00:58:33.980 align:middle line:84%
there, so you don't
know what to choose.

00:58:33.980 --> 00:58:35.450 align:middle line:84%
You're choosing
sometimes positive

00:58:35.450 --> 00:58:36.980 align:middle line:90%
while negative is following you.

00:58:36.980 --> 00:58:40.360 align:middle line:84%
Or you might choose negative to
punish yourself or someone else

00:58:40.360 --> 00:58:46.930 align:middle line:84%
while positive might come and
represent itself as whatever.

00:58:46.930 --> 00:58:49.100 align:middle line:84%
You see, the
complexity of reality

00:58:49.100 --> 00:58:53.200 align:middle line:84%
is the mind, the
way of the mind.

00:58:53.200 --> 00:58:57.700 align:middle line:84%
Simplicity of reality
is the way of no mind.

00:58:57.700 --> 00:58:59.130 align:middle line:84%
Everything is so
simple right now.

00:58:59.130 --> 00:59:01.630 align:middle line:90%
Life is happening right now.

00:59:01.630 --> 00:59:05.210 align:middle line:84%
Life is not happening
anywhere else apart from now.

00:59:05.210 --> 00:59:08.816 align:middle line:84%
So if you are right now,
you're very much alive.

00:59:08.816 --> 00:59:12.950 align:middle line:84%
If you have that awareness, if
you have that access to now,

00:59:12.950 --> 00:59:15.750 align:middle line:84%
then you will also realize
that you are infinite.

00:59:15.750 --> 00:59:18.220 align:middle line:84%
And when you are infinite,
there's no need to worry.

00:59:18.220 --> 00:59:19.640 align:middle line:90%
There's no need to be in fear.

00:59:19.640 --> 00:59:21.520 align:middle line:90%
There's no need to be anxious.

00:59:21.520 --> 00:59:24.350 align:middle line:84%
There's no need to separate
yourself and fantasize

00:59:24.350 --> 00:59:27.620 align:middle line:84%
about this and be
lost for some time.

00:59:27.620 --> 00:59:28.650 align:middle line:90%
You're present.

00:59:28.650 --> 00:59:33.600 align:middle line:84%
You see through everything
that appears in front of you.

00:59:33.600 --> 00:59:39.540 align:middle line:84%
So you see, if we are able to
see everything as illusion,

00:59:39.540 --> 00:59:44.700 align:middle line:84%
then we find ourselves real
at the end of the journey.

00:59:44.700 --> 00:59:46.530 align:middle line:84%
So everything you
are experiencing,

00:59:46.530 --> 00:59:48.640 align:middle line:84%
everything you are
seeing, everything

00:59:48.640 --> 00:59:54.280 align:middle line:84%
that appears and goes, it's
not real, and it's not you.

00:59:54.280 --> 00:59:54.940 align:middle line:90%
Do you get it?

00:59:54.940 --> 00:59:55.340 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:59:55.340 --> 00:59:56.464 align:middle line:90%
>>RADOS: It comes and goes.

00:59:56.464 --> 00:59:58.150 align:middle line:90%
It's a world of change.

00:59:58.150 --> 01:00:00.340 align:middle line:90%
You appear, you disappear.

01:00:00.340 --> 01:00:03.660 align:middle line:84%
I cannot remember-- we had an
interview, great interview.

01:00:03.660 --> 01:00:04.600 align:middle line:90%
You remember this.

01:00:04.600 --> 01:00:05.730 align:middle line:90%
I could not remember you.

01:00:05.730 --> 01:00:06.720 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I remember the
time, it was wonderful.

01:00:06.720 --> 01:00:07.420 align:middle line:90%
But, yes.

01:00:07.420 --> 01:00:09.030 align:middle line:84%
>>RADOS: But what
I could remember

01:00:09.030 --> 01:00:12.420 align:middle line:84%
is your absolute
assertive voice.

01:00:12.420 --> 01:00:17.210 align:middle line:10%
And I said, this
person is absolutely

01:00:17.210 --> 01:00:20.810 align:middle line:10%
stable in her own self, you see?

01:00:20.810 --> 01:00:22.310 align:middle line:90%
That's what you get.

01:00:22.310 --> 01:00:26.820 align:middle line:84%
Not the shapes and forms, but
the essence, the consciousness.

01:00:26.820 --> 01:00:29.000 align:middle line:84%
So your body's
different than my body.

01:00:29.000 --> 01:00:30.590 align:middle line:84%
Your mind has a
different structure

01:00:30.590 --> 01:00:33.960 align:middle line:84%
than my body-- than
my mind and my body.

01:00:33.960 --> 01:00:39.220 align:middle line:84%
Your emotions fluctuate
differently than my emotions.

01:00:39.220 --> 01:00:42.280 align:middle line:84%
We are different in
outside circumstances.

01:00:42.280 --> 01:00:45.430 align:middle line:84%
But we are one and
the same in oneness.

01:00:45.430 --> 01:00:47.650 align:middle line:84%
Your consciousness
and my consciousness

01:00:47.650 --> 01:00:49.200 align:middle line:90%
is one consciousness.

01:00:49.200 --> 01:00:51.790 align:middle line:84%
When you become conscious
of who you are and I

01:00:51.790 --> 01:00:55.400 align:middle line:84%
become conscious of who you are,
I'll recognize myself in you.

01:00:55.400 --> 01:00:59.500 align:middle line:84%
Because your consciousness
is all about goodness, peace,

01:00:59.500 --> 01:01:04.210 align:middle line:84%
tranquility, love, happiness,
contentment in the moment.

01:01:04.210 --> 01:01:05.800 align:middle line:90%
That's the same in me.

01:01:05.800 --> 01:01:08.190 align:middle line:90%
So I recognize myself in you.

01:01:08.190 --> 01:01:09.420 align:middle line:90%
And that's what love is.

01:01:09.420 --> 01:01:11.120 align:middle line:90%
I love you, you see?

01:01:11.120 --> 01:01:12.680 align:middle line:90%
And you love me.

01:01:12.680 --> 01:01:15.070 align:middle line:84%
Actually, I accept
you the way you are.

01:01:15.070 --> 01:01:18.100 align:middle line:84%
If you decide to go
a little bit dreamy,

01:01:18.100 --> 01:01:23.140 align:middle line:84%
go and confirm to society that
you are valuable, available,

01:01:23.140 --> 01:01:23.640 align:middle line:90%
part of it.

01:01:23.640 --> 01:01:24.600 align:middle line:90%
So find good.

01:01:24.600 --> 01:01:25.450 align:middle line:90%
I'm OK with that.

01:01:25.450 --> 01:01:29.160 align:middle line:84%
And I will wait the moment
when I will recognize myself

01:01:29.160 --> 01:01:30.800 align:middle line:84%
in you again, and
we'll be together,

01:01:30.800 --> 01:01:34.600 align:middle line:84%
and love will be
there to be shared.

01:01:34.600 --> 01:01:35.360 align:middle line:90%
Do you get it?

01:01:35.360 --> 01:01:36.250 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I do.

01:01:36.250 --> 01:01:37.830 align:middle line:90%
And-- wow.

01:01:37.830 --> 01:01:38.330 align:middle line:90%
OK.

