We actually went over time.

01:01:40.260 --> 01:01:42.134 align:middle line:84%
I've enjoyed myself so
much because I've just

01:01:42.134 --> 01:01:44.190 align:middle line:84%
been floating in the
right hemisphere,

01:01:44.190 --> 01:01:46.110 align:middle line:84%
